                    </svg>
                .mission__content-info-second
                    p 
                        |   “There were dozens of retail bankruptcies in 2020, and experts say the pain isn't over yet. S&P Global Market Intelligence tallied 49 bankruptcies in the retail space as of mid-November, including Ann Taylor parent Ascena Retail Group Inc.”